					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Treat the 1s and 0s in loopy's scrolling document as <em>bit masks</em> - that is, transfer the "1" bits on the left to the "1" bits on the right, in the same order (and leave the "0" bits alone).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
