					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The '1' bits get copied over, and the '0' bits are <em>ignored</em>. The ONLY bits that get <strong>cleared</strong> are the upper 2 bits during the first write to $2006 (the lower of which is the high order bit for fine vertical scroll).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
